    &gt;LINE Notify&lt;/a&gt;👆登入後選擇&lt;code&gt;個人頁面&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.jameshost.org/p/line%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E9%80%9F%E5%A0%B1/me.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1919&#34;
	height=&#34;914&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://blog.jameshost.org/p/line%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E9%80%9F%E5%A0%B1/me_hu0de60e819b928503134b0a15309411a7_68465_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://blog.jameshost.org/p/line%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E9%80%9F%E5%A0%B1/me_hu0de60e819b928503134b0a15309411a7_68465_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
